situation: I've had trouble sleeping the last few nights, I feel really low self esteem.

final_result.label: normal
final_result.response: It's great that you're considering reaching out for support! You might find it helpful to think about what would make you feel more comfortable. Would you prefer to get some encouragement from your friends first, or do you think starting to write on your own might help build your confidence? Both options have their merits, so it really depends on how you feel right now.
